Fabinho, Nildo. (Coach: Luís Felipe)

10/08/1994 Grêmio 1-0 Ceará
                   Nildo  3'   (1-0)
Referee: Oscar Roberto de Godói
Att: 49 263
Grêmio: Danrlei, Ayupe, Paulão, Agnaldo, Roger - Pingo, Jamir, Émerson, Carlos Miguel
(Wallace) - Fabinho, Nildo (Carlinhos). (Coach: Luís Felipe)
